---
title: Beef Tenderloin & Gouda Sandos plus Balsamic Au Jus & Mixed Greens Salad with Apple
description: Dip dip hooray! Celebrate dinnertime with a twist on this classic hot sammie. Our chefs swapped out the traditional roast beef and layered luxurious seared beef tenderloin, melty Gouda, and pickled shallots between Dijonnaise-spread toasted sourdough–a sandwich fit for dinner. Serve a bright green salad with apples for fresh crunch on the side, plus a deep beefy-balsamic broth for dipping. Dunk, soak, swirl, repeat—this French dip just can’t be beat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-tenderloin-gouda-sandos-b7581a5b.jpg
